<FONT size=4 color=#000000> "Talitha Cumi"<BR>
        Story:    David Duchovny & Chris Carter<BR>
        Teleplay: Chris Carter<BR>
        Director: Robert W. Goodwin<BR>
        Location: Quonochontaug, Rhode Island<BR>
        After a crazed gunman opens fire on members of the public in a<BR>
   restaurant, a strange man miraculously cures the victims, and then<BR>
   disappears. When Mulder's mother suffers a heart attack, Mulder and<BR>
   Scully track down the mysterious healer. Unfortunately, an alien bounty<BR>
   hunter also wants the healer, and will stop at nothing to keep the<BR>
   secret hiden.<BR>
        Jeremiah Smith ..................... Roy Thinnes<BR>
        William Mulder ..................... Peter Donat<BR>
        Munse .............................. Brian Thompson<BR>
        Mrs Mulder ......................... Rebecca Toolan<BR>
<BR>
   (Part 1 of 2 part story)<BR>
<BR>
   -NOTE<BR>
      "Talitha Cumi" are the word used by Jesus when he raised a girl from<BR>
the dead in the New Testament.<BR>
<BR>
   -NOTE<BR>
      Roy Thinnes, who plays Jeremiah Smith in this episode, also appeared<BR>
in the US SciFi/Alien TV Series 'The Invaders'.<BR>
